## Legacy Hospitality Authorization Form & Process

Please follow this process for hospitality provided:

* While on travel status;
* To be paid via university travel card or p-card;
* Paid out-of-pocket and to be reimbursed; OR
* If hospitality is provided prior to January 26, 2026, and paid directly from the university to a vendor, including university auxiliary organizations.
